children.text: Ghost Sighting - Scarily Honest Reviews - YouTube
Review by PhysicalGraffiti007, read by Courtney Ryan Law.
"He knew nothing of the history of hauntings, nor did I..."
"...he was tall, thin and dressed in 1800's attire..."
"...I cried out, but couldn't move and couldn't scream."
"If you asked me if I'd return, I'd tell you I'm not sure... I'd only do so with great trepidation."
